description: 2022 Election LIVE News, Uttar Pradesh, Uttarakhand, Manipur, Goa and Punjab Election Latest Updates: Meanwhile, a voter turnout of over 78% was recorded in Goa on Monday. The turnout in Uttar Pradesh and Uttarakhand, according to data received till 5 pm, was over 60% and 59.37% respectively.
